PyroCMS
=======

VERSION: 0.9-pre-alpha
AUTHOR: Philip Sturgeon < email@philsturgeon.co.uk >

DESCRIPTION
-----------

PyroCMS is a CMS built using the CodeIgniter PHP framework with modularity in mind. Lightweight, themeable and dynamic.


INSTALLATION
------------

See INSTALL file for step-by-step installation instructions.


BUGS / FEATURE REQUESTS
-----------------------

This project has a ticket/milestone planning page located at the URL below. Before reporting bugs or requesting any features, please check there is not already a ticket.

    http://www.assembla.com/spaces/pyrocms/tickets

If there is no ticket, please send an e-mail to < email@philsturgeon.co.uk >.